rai\" class=\"wp-image-9120\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/720999e1a3b459ea00a5_result-1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/720999e1a3b459ea00a5_result-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/720999e1a3b459ea00a5_result-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/720999e1a3b459ea00a5_result-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/720999e1a3b459ea00a5_result-1-450x253.jpg 450w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/720999e1a3b459ea00a5_result-1-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/720999e1a3b459ea00a5_result-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption><em>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gam m\u00e0u \u0111\u01a1n s\u1eafc t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh b\u00f3ng&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 t\u00ednh b\u00f3ng trong n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 k\u00ednh, b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ph\u1ee7 Acrylic, Acrylic Mirror,&#8230;B\u1edfi nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u b\u00f3ng trong phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00fac x\u1ea1 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1t, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng khu v\u1ef1c b\u1ebfp. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean g\u1ea1ch men \u1ed1p t\u01b0\u1eddng hay \u0111\u1ed3 s\u1ee9 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c v\u00e0 cho ta c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t.&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"435\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/92c5732e66098057d918-1024x435.jpg\" alt=\"vat-lieu-bong-guong-giup-nhan-rong-dien-tich-phong-bep\" class=\"wp-image-9121\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/92c5732e66098057d918-1024x435.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/92c5732e66098057d918-300x128.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/92c5732e66098057d918-768x326.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/92c5732e66098057d918-1536x653.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/92c5732e66098057d918.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption><em>V\u1eadt li\u1ec7u b\u00f3ng g\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00fap nh\u00e2n r\u1ed9ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t, b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cho ta c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean hi\u1ec7n nay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp n\u00e0o c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00f3 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp.&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/1-1-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"anh-sang-la-yeu-to-quan-trong-trong-viec-bo-tri-noi-that-bep\" class=\"wp-image-9122\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/1-1-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/1-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/1-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/1-1-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/1-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption><em>\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ebfp<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfu to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng cho ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap nh\u00e2n r\u1ed9ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1ed1i \u0111a. Khu v\u1ef1c b\u1ed3n r\u1eeda v\u00e0 b\u1ebfp n\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ngu\u1ed3n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ea5u n\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch. Do \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1eadp trung kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c b\u1ebfp n\u00fac tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t, b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>\u01afu ti\u00ean v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9, phong th\u1ee7y an to\u00e0n th\u00ec m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c gia ch\u1ee7 quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u00ec v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 g\u1ed7, \u0111\u00e1, g\u1ea1ch, k\u00ednh, kim lo\u1ea1i&#8230;lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"788\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/35b2e89aeef209ac50e3-1024x788.jpg\" alt=\"khu-vuc-nau-nuong-duoc-toi-uu-cong-nang-tien-nghi\" class=\"wp-image-9123\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/35b2e89aeef209ac50e3-1024x788.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/35b2e89aeef209ac50e3-300x231.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/35b2e89aeef209ac50e3-768x591.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/35b2e89aeef209ac50e3-1536x1183.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/35b2e89aeef209ac50e3.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption><em>Khu v\u1ef1c n\u1ea5u n\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng ti\u1ec7n nghi<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u trong ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao v\u1ec1 th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng. Trong \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a g\u1ed7 &#8211; \u0111\u00e1 &#8211; k\u00ednh lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi v\u1ebb sang tr\u1ecdng, cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c lu\u00f4n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng m\u1eb9o hay v\u1ec1 trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\">Byzan Interior<\/a> \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp nh\u1ecf h\u1eb9p tr\u1edf n\u00ean ti\u1ec7n nghi, r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i v\u00e0 tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/phong-cach-noi-that-dan-dau-xu-huong-nam-2020\/\">Phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng 2020<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/xu-hong-thiet-ke-noi-that-phong-ngu\/\">Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 2020<\/a><\/strong><br><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ebfp n\u1ea5u lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201ctr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0\u201d v\u00e0 b\u1ebfp c\u00f3 \u1ea5m, nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi an. V\u00ec v\u1eady trong m\u1ed7i d\u1ef1 \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ch\u1ee7 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh nh\u00e0 \u1edf ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay nh\u01b0 chung c\u01b0,&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":9124,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-9115","post","type-post","status-publish","format-stan